FROM VRAP.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_HDR DH INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_HDR RH ON DH.RECN_GID=RH.RECN_GID INNER JOIN VRAP.TVNDR TV ON RH.VEND_ID=TV.VNDR_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_SUMM DS ON DH.DSTR_GID=DS.DSTR_GID

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT DH.DSTR_GID, TV.CORP_CD, DH.RECN_GID , DH.DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD , RA.DSTRBN_RSN_CD AS DSTRBN_RSN_CD, DH.DSTR_STAT_CD AS DSTRBN_STUS_CD, CASE WHEN DH.DSTR_STAT_CD = 2 THEN DDP.APRV_PEND_ROLE_CD WHEN DH.DSTR_STAT_CD = 98 THEN -2 ELSE -1 END AS DSTRBN_PEND_RLE_CD, (DH.XMIT_PMT_TS) AS DSTRBN_RPS_TRN_DT, (DH.XMIT_GL_TS) AS DSTRBN_SAP_TRN_DT, DH.POST_DT AS DSTRBN_SAP_POST_DT, DATE(ADTL.MAX_DSTRBN_ACT_DT) AS DSTRBN_ACT_DT, DATE(DH.INSRT_TS) AS DSTRBN_CRTE_DT, DH.INSRT_USER_ID AS DSTRBN_CRTE_USR_ID, DH.UP_TO_INV_CD, DH.INCL_DSPT_PD_CD, DH.INCL_DSPT_ADJ_CD AS DSTRBN_IN_ADJ_IN, DH.WHLD_ADJ_CD AS DSTRBN_WTH_ADJ_IN , DH.DISC_PMT_PCT AS DSTRBN_PMT_PCT, DS.ADMN_PEND_DSTR_AMT , DS.ADMN_PRIR_DSTR_AMT , DS.BASE_PEND_DSTR_AMT , DS.BASE_PRIR_DSTR_AMT , DS.PERF_PEND_DSTR_AMT , DS.PERF_PRIR_DSTR_AMT , DS.FRMLY_PEND_DSTR_AMT , DS.FRMLY_PRIR_DSTR_AMT , DS.CTRC_PEND_DSTR_AMT , DS.CTRC_PRIR_DSTR_AMT , DS.PRC_PTCT_PEND_DSTR_AMT , DS.PRC_PTCT_PRIR_DSTR_AMT , DS.ADMN_PEND_ADJ_AMT , DS.ADMN_PRIR_ADJ_AMT , DS.BASE_PEND_ADJ_AMT , DS.BASE_PRIR_ADJ_AMT , DS.PERF_PEND_ADJ_AMT , DS.PERF_PRIR_ADJ_AMT , DS.FRMLY_PEND_ADJ_AMT , DS.FRMLY_PRIR_ADJ_AMT , DS.CTRC_PEND_ADJ_AMT , DS.CTRC_PRIR_ADJ_AMT , DS.PRC_PTCT_PEND_ADJ_AMT , DS.PRC_PTCT_PRIR_ADJ_AMT , DD1.APRV_RECV_USER_ID , DD2.APRV_RECV_USER_ID , DD3.APRV_RECV_USER_ID , DD4.APRV_RECV_USER_ID , DD5.APRV_RECV_USER_ID , DD6.APRV_RECV_USER_ID , DD1.APRV_ACTN_CD , DD2.APRV_ACTN_CD , DD3.APRV_ACTN_CD , DD4.APRV_ACTN_CD , DD5.APRV_ACTN_CD , DD6.APRV_ACTN_CD , CASE WHEN DD5.APRV_ACTN_CD=2 THEN -1 ELSE DD6.PRXY_APRV_CD END PRXY_APRV_CD, DD1.APRV_RECV_TS, DD2.APRV_RECV_TS, DD3.APRV_RECV_TS, DD4.APRV_RECV_TS, DD5.APRV_RECV_TS, DD6.APRV_RECV_TS, DS.LAST_UPDT_TS
FROM VRAP.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_HDR DH INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_HDR RH ON DH.RECN_GID=RH.RECN_GID INNER JOIN VRAP.TVNDR TV ON RH.VEND_ID=TV.VNDR_ID
INNER JOIN (SELECT DRA.DSTR_GID,MAX(DRA.DSTR_REAS_CD) AS DSTRBN_RSN_CD FROM VRAP.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_REAS_ASSC DRA GROUP BY DRA.DSTR_GID )RA
ON DH.DSTR_GID=RA.DSTR_GID INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_SUMM DS ON DH.DSTR_GID=DS.DSTR_GID INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL DD1 ON DH.DSTR_GID=DD1.DSTR_GID AND DD1.APRV_ROLE_CD=1 INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL DD2 ON DH.DSTR_GID=DD2.DSTR_GID AND DD2.APRV_ROLE_CD=2 INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL DD3 ON DH.DSTR_GID=DD3.DSTR_GID AND DD3.APRV_ROLE_CD=3 INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL DD4 ON DH.DSTR_GID=DD4.DSTR_GID AND DD4.APRV_ROLE_CD=4 INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL DD5 ON DH.DSTR_GID=DD5.DSTR_GID AND DD5.APRV_ROLE_CD=5 INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL DD6 ON DH.DSTR_GID=DD6.DSTR_GID AND DD6.APRV_ROLE_CD=6 INNER JOIN (SELECT Z.DSTR_GID,MAX(Z.APRV_RECV_TS) MAX_DSTRBN_ACT_DT FROM VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL Z group by Z.DSTR_GID) ADTL ON DH.DSTR_GID=ADTL.DSTR_GID
LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.DSTR_GID,X.PRXY_APRV_CD PRXY_APRV_CD, MIN(X.APRV_ROLE_CD) APRV_PEND_ROLE_CD FROM VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL X WHERE X.APRV_ACTN_CD = 1 GROUP BY X.DSTR_GID,X.PRXY_APRV_CD) DDP ON DH.DSTR_GID=DDP.DSTR_GID
WHERE (DH.UPDT_TS>TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS_UT') OR DD1.APRV_RECV_TS >TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS_AA_ACT') OR DD2.APRV_RECV_TS >TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS_MA_ACT') OR DD3.APRV_RECV_TS >TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS_DA_ACT') OR DD4.APRV_RECV_TS >TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS_VPA_ACT') OR DD5.APRV_RECV_TS >TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS_CA') OR DD6.APRV_RECV_TS >TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS_CMA') OR DS.LAST_UPDT_TS >TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS_LUT')) AND DH.DSTR_STAT_CD IN (2,90,98)
WITH UR
